          en: "HydraFacial is a patented system that combines multiple actions in one procedure through specialised device tips:\n\nStep 1 — Cleanse + Peel:\nGentle exfoliation of the surface dead-cell layer using a combination of gluconolactone (PHA acid) and salicylic acid — at concentrations that deliver results without causing redness.\n\nStep 2 — Extract + Hydrate:\nThe Vortex tip simultaneously:\n— uses vacuum to extract pore contents (comedones, sebaceous plugs) without mechanical pressure;\n— infuses a hydrating serum into the pores.\n\nStep 3 — Fuse + Protect:\nA final antioxidant complex (hyaluronic acid + peptides + AGF — autologous growth factor or plant-based equivalent) is delivered into the skin via the vortex method — deeper than topical application.\n\nWhy HydraFacial differs from device peels or manual extraction:\n— Manual extraction: mechanical pressure, redness for 1-2 days, pore trauma risk;\n— Ultrasound facial: surface only, doesn't clear deep comedones;\n— Chemical peel: exfoliation without deep pore cleansing;\n— HydraFacial: cleansing + hydration + exfoliation in one painless session.\n\nResult after one session: fresh, even, hydrated skin with visibly cleaner pores. No redness, no raw look. You can walk out without makeup immediately.",
